	<div class="cuh">
	Many projects that aim to fix and address problems connected to climate change have already been conducted. An example of this is "Regenerate Australia"-- a project that hopes to raise money
	for the restoration of Australia's ecostsyems after the wild bushfires during the years 2019-2020. Though not all of us may be able to launch or participate in huge projects such as Regenerate
	Australia, it is important to know what we are capable of. Joining small fundraisers for cleaning coastal roads or beaches, conserving energy, trying to use less machines who's byproducts may harm
	the atmosphere already make a huge impact. With this, here are some extraordinary projects created that were made for the betterment of our planet:
	</div>
